{"tid":2458163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE粉絲超狂！為偶像豪建8棟樓 「子瑜樓」施工中","createTime":"2021-03-23T08:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T08:27:17.000Z","uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3719c05cfab3255b5e73e5d223158a5709da7d04","tid":2458163,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6jKBAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6jKBAR.jpg&h=71370278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓當紅九人女團TWICE成員包含娜璉、定延、志效、多賢、彩瑛、Momo、Sana、Mina以及台灣籍成員子瑜，在海內外享有超高人氣，每每推出新曲，總是橫掃各大排行榜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k2gQw9h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk2gQw9h.jpg&h=818d8c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有超狂粉絲建造房子，以TWICE成員名字命名。（翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n近期，就有粉絲在網路上分享照片，他在仁川建造了8棟房子，並且全部都以成員名字來命名，引發關注。圖中可以看見不同造型的大樓，都掛上大大的招牌寫著：「Momo House」、<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">「娜璉House」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDj6PWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDj6PWi.jpg&h=f3c8e7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsbAJgx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsbAJgx.png&h=c7a17813&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrJO3gy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjrJO3gy.png&h=3b5ccdee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rJb5k3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrJb5k3f.png&h=119b83c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n、<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">「定延House」</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JLHoR97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJLHoR97.jpg&h=a43f688a&s={SIZE}\" />等，並且該粉絲也提到，現在只有8棟建築物，是因為以子瑜命名的房子尚未完工。<br />\n<br />\n網友看見TWICE超瘋狂壯舉，紛紛留言表示「哇！我也要替我偶像蓋樓」、「人生終於有目標了」、「我飯NCT（南韓男團，有23名成員），那要建造23棟樓嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3474716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3474716&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97f7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=d519ac79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3474716&h=9e1f63f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3474716</a>"},{"pid":"bf3b46721d356a93a6f65a463817473916169bb7","tid":2458163,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:25:40.000Z","msg":"「子瑜樓」=PRC大使館?"},{"pid":"99ab2efa9485cd9a4c87958b5caa7b01b29dd365","tid":2458163,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:27:17.000Z","msg":"K POP粉真係弱智"}]}